      <title>苹果将​​推出密码应用程序，挑战 1Password 和 LastPass</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/apple-to-debut-passwords-app-in-challenge-to-1password-lastpass</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，苹果公司将于下周推出一款名为“Passwords”的全新自主研发应用程序，旨在让客户更轻松地登录网站和软件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/apple-to-debut-passwords-app-in-challenge-to-1password-lastpass</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 20:16:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>硅谷对加州拟议的人工智能法案保持警惕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-06-06/silicon-valley-is-on-alert-over-an-ai-bill-in-california</link>
      <description><![CDATA[批评人士担心，该法案可能会给开发商带来难以承受的负担，迫使他们保证自己的服务不被不良分子滥用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-06-06/silicon-valley-is-on-alert-over-an-ai-bill-in-california</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 20:09:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>秘密资金曝光后，Optica 切断与华为的合作关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/optica-foundation-cuts-ties-with-huawei-after-bloomberg-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博新闻社报道华为技术有限公司秘密资助美国大学尖端研究竞赛项目后，Optica 基金会首席执行官表示，该基金会将不再接受华为技术有限公司的资金用于资助美国大学尖端研究的竞赛。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/optica-foundation-cuts-ties-with-huawei-after-bloomberg-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 19:33:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国科技大亨林奇在美国审判中摆脱惠普欺诈指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/uk-tech-tycoon-mike-lynch-cleared-of-fraud-charges-in-us-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国科技大亨迈克·林奇被控 13 年前欺骗惠普公司以 110 亿美元收购其软件初创公司，制造了硅谷有史以来最大的欺诈案，但最终被判无罪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/uk-tech-tycoon-mike-lynch-cleared-of-fraud-charges-in-us-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 18:57:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
